text: Devind Pathmanathan (born 17 February 1995) is a Sri Lankan cricketer. He made his Twenty20 debut for Kalutara Town Club in the 2017–18 SLC Twenty20 Tournament on 24 February 2018. His uncle, Gajan Pathmanathan, was a first- class cricketer. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1995 births Category:Kalutara Town Club cricketers Category:Living people Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Sri Lankan cricketers
